author: Dan Waites
title: In Pictures: Gazans take no chances as coronavirus threat looms
description: Authorities and residents in Gaza are behaving as if virus is already a threat to prevent potential catastrophe.
content:
Gaza City - An outbreak of COVID-19 in the Gaza Strip would be catastrophic. Critical shortages of drugs, protective equipment, testing materials and ventilators in Gazan hospitals mean Gazans would be quickly overwhelmed by an outbreak of the virus.
